# Voice feedback widget (issue #43) — server-side only, never commit real values.
# Get a key at https://elevenlabs.io — used by api/tts.js to synthesize the
# assistant's spoken questions. Set via `vercel env add`, not in this file.
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=
# Optional — defaults to a neutral built-in voice if unset. See
# https://elevenlabs.io/docs/api-reference/voices for available voice IDs.
ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID=

# Get a key at https://console.groq.com — used by api/next-turn.js (picks
# follow-up questions) and api/file-feedback.js (extracts the session
# summary before filing a ticket).
GROQ_API_KEY=

# CLASSIC GitHub PAT (not fine-grained) with the `gist` + `repo` scopes.
# Used by api/file-feedback.js to file the session summary as a Pending
# ticket AND to create a secret Gist of the full transcript for
# cross-session review — Gist creation requires the classic `gist` OAuth
# scope, which fine-grained PATs cannot grant at all. `repo` is broader
# than ideal (classic PATs don't support per-repo scoping) but is the only
# way to also cover issue creation + project board mutations with one
# token. Deliberately separate from any token used by the agent-dispatch
# pipeline (agent-dispatch/README.md).
GITHUB_TOKEN=
